high_descs: Turn around and cross the room to the sink.
Pick up the spoon from the drying rack on the left side of the sink.
Move a step to the right while carrying the spoon.
Put the spoon in the right side of the sink, turn on the water, and then remove it once rinsed.
Turn left and move to the counter just to the right of the dishwasher.
Place the spoon on the counter in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed spoon on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and walk across the room to face the sink.
Pick up the spoon on the left side of the sink.
Take a step to the right to face the right side of the sink.
Wash the spoon in the sink and then remove it.
Turn left and step forward to face the counter.
Place the spoon on the counter.
anns.task_desc: To wash a spoon and place it on the counter to the right of the sink.

high_descs: Make your way over to the kitchen sink.
Pick up the metal table spoon off of the counter to the left of the sink.
Turn right and walk forward, then turn left to face the sink.
Put the metal spoon in the sink and turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn the water off and remove the spoon.
Turn left and walk over to the counter.
Put the clean spoon on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean spoon on the counter.
